<p>
<lb n="1"/><hi rend="bold">pārthiva saṁvatsarada</hi> Ā
<lb n="2" break="no"/><hi rend="bold">śvija ba 7 lu</hi> ceṁḍikeya narasa<unclear>yya</unclear>
<lb n="3" break="no"/>gaḷa voṁmaga kē<unclear>ṣa</unclear>
<lb n="4" break="no"/>vaṁṇanu kāṁdalavā
<lb n="5" break="no"/>ḍi lakṣīnārāyaṇa dē
<lb n="6" break="no"/>varige māḍisida garu
<lb n="7" break="no"/>ḍagaṁbha sēve
</p>

<!--<h4>B.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="1"/><hi rend="bold">pārthiva saṁvatsarada Āśvija ba <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> </hi>
<lb n="2"/>kaḷasayigaḷa tiṁmapagaḷa ma
<lb n="3" break="no"/>kkaḷu <unclear>giriya</unclear> payanavaru na<unclear>rā</unclear>
<lb n="4" break="no"/>ṇapurada lakṣīnārāyaṇa dē
<lb n="5" break="no"/><unclear>vaṟi</unclear> ge guḍikaṭṭi<unclear>si</unclear>
<lb n="6" break="no"/>da sēve śrī
</p>

